description: The ETH Low Volatility Set is for you if you believe the price of Ether will swing within a smaller range in the medium to long term. This Set automatically rebalances cash (DAI) into ETH if the price of ETH dips more than 30% and ETH into cash (DAI) if the price of ETH rebounds more than 35%. The token tolerances are selected to balance profit against risk, preventing token holders from selling into a rally (or buying into a drop) yet still taking profits when the downside of missing a trade is too high.
name: ETH Range Bound Low Volatility Set
